title: Match facts: Malmo FF v Real Madrid (UEFA Champions League) - World
text:
Related UEFA Champions League group stage results & scorers (2nd matchday) Full time: Malmo 0-2 Real Madrid
Scorer: Ronaldo 29, 90
Yellow cards: Rosenberg 21, Berget 36, Yotun 36 (Malmo)/ Kovacic 11, Casemiro 37 (Real Madrid)
Red cards: Yotun 78 (Malmo)
Starting lineups
Malmo : Johan Wiland, Anton Tinnerholm, Yoshimar Yotun, Rasmus Bengtsson, Kari Arnason, Oscar Lewicki, Kofi Adu, Vladimir Rodic (Magnus Wolff Eikrem 67), Markus Rosenberg, Inge Berget, Nikola Djurdji (Felipe Carvalho 81)
Real Madrid : Keylor Navas, Raphael Varane, Nacho, Cristiano Ronaldo, Toni Kroos, Karim Benzema (Luka Modric 67), Casemiro, Dani Carvajal, Mateo Kovacic (Lucas Vazquez 73), Alvaro Arbeloa, Isco (Denis Cheryshev 84)
Venue: Swedbank Stadion (Malmo)
Referee: Cüneyt Çakır (TUR)
